704452f-a.title: Brooklyn: Front Street - Jay Street
704452f-a.text:
Fhont Street, south side, east from Jay Street. Also shown, is Jay
Street, at, adjoining and south of the S.E. corner of Front Street, as seen
across Vacant lot at the S.W. corner. Occupants of same, are the National
Lead Co., and Brooklyn Edison Co. (Station 44).
March 9, 1937.
. Sperr.  RO N88PRODUCTIONS.
